                           / assist (plaver name)<br>
                           /attack %t<br>
                           / doability 4 (for my 2-hand bash)<br>
<br>
Healme                /target (my name)<br>
                         /doability 4 (my 2-hand bash for stun)<br>
                         /cast 6<br>
                       <br>
For BMB Requests  /rt &quot;incoming BMB&quot; (tells them it's  <br>
